item.title: result<>
item.description: Outcome 2.0 namespace It is recommended that you refer to entities from this Outcome 2.0 via the following namespace alias: namespace outcome = OUTCOME_V2_NAMESPACE; View this code on Github As patches and modifications are applied to this library, namespaces get permuted in order not to break any backward compatibility. At some point namespace outcome::v2 will be defined, and this will be the prefered namespace. Until then OUTCOME_V2_NAMESPACE denotes the most recently updated version, getting closer to outcome::v2.
